title: The Pythagorean Theorem - 4 Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 4 books on the Pythagorean theorem in PDF format with OCR & cover:

1. Pythagorean Triangle - or The Science of Numbers by George Oliver (4.77 mb, 1875)
2. The Pythagorean Proposition by Elisha S. Loomis (9.39 mb, 1940)
3. The Pythagorean Theorem - A 4,000 Year History by Eli Maor (10.3 mb, 2007)
4. The Pythagorean Theorem - Crown Jewel of Mathematics by John C. Sparks (1.93 mb, 2008)
